<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 01:42:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>我们对 Polymarket 典型用户的了解</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/22/what-we-know-about-the-typical-polymarket-user/</link><description>在我们的研究期间，典型的 Polymarket 用户在 10 个活跃交易日内总共进行了 46 笔交易。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 01:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/22/what-we-know-about-the-typical-polymarket-user/</guid></item><item><title>中等收入国家的人们如何看待美国削减人道主义援助？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/21/what-do-people-in-middle-income-countries-think-about-cuts-to-us-humanitarian-aid/</link><description>在接受调查的 16 个中等收入国家中，许多人不确定美国人道主义援助削减将给他们带来什么影响，但持负面看法的人也不少。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 01:23:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/21/what-do-people-in-middle-income-countries-think-about-cuts-to-us-humanitarian-aid/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普第二届政府期间美国对外援助大幅下降</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/21/us-foreign-aid-is-plunging-in-second-trump-administration/</link><description>2025 财年，美国对外援助经通胀调整后降至 20 多年来的最低水平，降至 473 亿美元，比上一年减少逾 240 亿美元。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 01:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/21/us-foreign-aid-is-plunging-in-second-trump-administration/</guid></item><item><title>六张图表显示全球能源生产正在发生怎样的变化</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/20/how-global-energy-production-is-changing-in-6-charts/</link><description>化石燃料仍然在全球电力中占主导地位，但风能和太阳能正在蓬勃发展。 2025 年，全球可再生能源首次超过煤炭，提供 34% 的电力。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 01:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/20/how-global-energy-production-is-changing-in-6-charts/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国人表示，当今的年轻人更难实现关键的财务里程碑</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/17/majorities-of-americans-say-key-financial-milestones-are-harder-for-todays-young-adults-to-reach/</link><description>大多数美国人表示，年轻人找工作、买房子、支付大学费用以及为未来储蓄比他们的父辈更难。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 01:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/17/majorities-of-americans-say-key-financial-milestones-are-harder-for-todays-young-adults-to-reach/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥人对克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆总统的好感度有所下降，但不如 2025 年</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/16/mexicans-view-president-claudia-sheinbaum-favorably-but-less-so-than-in-2025/</link><description>墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆仍然受欢迎，但她的好感度已降至 64%。对经济和民主的看法也在下降。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:27:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/07/16/mexicans-view-president-claudia-sheinbaum-favorably-but-less-so-than-in-2025/</guid></item><item><title>我们如何衡量美国人对公共生活的参与度</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/07/16/how-we-measured-americans-engagement-in-public-life/</link><description>本文解释了研究人员如何使用多模式调查、基于地址的抽样和聚类分析来衡量美国人对公共生活的参与度。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/decoded/2026/07/16/how-we-measured-americans-engagement-in-public-life/</guid></item><item><title>美国人如何参与新闻、政治、宗教和公民生活</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/07/16/how-americans-are-engaged-with-news-politics-religion-and-civic-life/</link><description>美国人与他人的交往并不是一维的。相反，他们分为四个不同的群体，反映了不同的社会参与模式。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/journalism/2026/07/16/how-americans-are-engaged-with-news-politics-religion-and-civic-life/</guid></item><item><title>现在许多国家的人们对中国的看法比美国更加积极</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/people-in-many-countries-now-view-china-more-positively-than-the-u-s/</link><description>最近，人们对中国的看法有所改善，而对美国的看法则有所恶化，目前大多数受访国家对中国的看法比美国更积极。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 01:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/people-in-many-countries-now-view-china-more-positively-than-the-u-s/</guid></item><item><title>全球对中国和习近平的看法正在改善</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/views-of-china-and-xi-are-improving-globally/</link><description>越来越多的人对中国抱有好感，对习近平充满信心，但富裕国家的看法却不那么积极。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/07/15/views-of-china-and-xi-are-improving-globally/</guid></item></channel></rss>